# Macro opener
this is a macro opener for bee swarm simulator 

# How to use

step one! make a discord bot! at (https://discord.com/developers/applications)
make sure the bot has Message Content Intent on!
invite it to at least one server. (to be safe)
open Macro Opener input your discord bot token.
then input your user id.
how to get your user id:
enable dev mode on discord and right click your profile and click copy user id.
for the command trigger i suggest !OM but you can use anything!
then hit browse and click your macro (revo has been tested natro has not been.)
then chose if you want the gui on start up or just the bot starting up or neither! (you can turn both on)
then hit start/stop bot!
